OL,3,CGoogle scraps diversity hiring targets
OL,5,FGoogle is scrapping its goal to hire
OL,6,Fmore members of staff from
OL,7,Fhistorically underrepresented groups
OL,8,Fand is reviewing its diversity,
OL,9,Fequity, and inclusion (DEI) targets.
OL,11,FThe tech giant follows companies such
OL,12,Fas Meta (owner of Facebook, WhatsApp
OL,13,Fand Instagram), Amazon, and McDonald's
OL,14,Fin rethinking their approach to
OL,15,Fdiversity initiatives.
