OL,3,CGoogle scraps diversity hiring targets
OL,5,FAfter years of pushing for more
OL,6,Finclusive policies, corporate America
OL,7,Fis shifting back towards more
OL,8,Fconservative social and political
OL,9,Fstances in response to the start of
OL,10,FDonald Trump's second administration.
OL,12,FIn an email to employees, Google said
OL,13,Fit would no longer have the
OL,14,F"aspirational goals" it previously set
OL,15,Fto improve representation, the Wall
OL,16,FStreet Journal reported.
