OL,3,CGoogle scraps diversity hiring targets
OL,5,FAnd in its annual report released this
OL,6,Fweek, Google's parent company Alphabet
OL,7,Fomitted a sentence that had been
OL,8,Fincluded in previous reports, stating
OL,9,Fthat it was "committed to making
OL,10,Fdiversity, equity, and inclusion part
OL,11,Fof everything we do and to growing a
OL,12,Fworkforce that is representative of
OL,13,Fthe users we serve".
OL,15,FThat statement had appeared in its
OL,16,Fannual reports from 2021 to 2023.
