OL,3,CGoogle scraps diversity hiring targets
OL,5,FGoogle issued a statement after the
OL,6,Fnews broke: "We're committed to
OL,7,Fcreating a workplace where all our
OL,8,Femployees can succeed and have equal
OL,9,Fopportunities, and over the last year
OL,10,Fwe've been reviewing our programmes
OL,11,Fdesigned to help us get there.
OL,13,F"We've updated our 10-k language to
OL,14,Freflect this, and as a federal
OL,15,Fcontractor, our teams are also
OL,16,Fevaluating changes required following
OL,17,Frecent court decisions and executive
OL,18,Forders on this topic."
