OL,3,CGoogle scraps diversity hiring targets
OL,5,FThe company said it was evaluating
OL,6,Fwhether to continue releasing annual
OL,7,Fdiversity reports, which it has done
OL,8,Fsince 2014.
OL,10,FIts 2024 diversity report said women
OL,11,Fmade up 34.1% of Google employees
OL,12,Fglobally in 2024, up from 30.6% in
OL,13,F2014. 5.7% of its US employees were
OL,14,Fblack and 7.5% were Latino, up from
OL,15,F2.4% and 4.5% respectively a decade
OL,16,Fearlier.
OL,18,FIt remains unclear how the changes
OL,19,Fwill affect the UK's workforce but
OL,20,Fcompanies must still comply with the
OL,21,Fcountry's equality laws.
