OL,3,CGoogle scraps diversity hiring targets
OL,5,FRachel Curley, deputy general
OL,6,Fsecretary of tech union Prospect,
OL,7,Fsaid: "Tech companies like Google,
OL,8,Fwhose US owners are changing
OL,9,Femployment practices to fit with the
OL,10,Fnew Trump administration, need to be
OL,11,Faware that employment law operates
OL,12,Fvery differently in the UK. There are
OL,13,Falso differing appetites for measures
OL,14,Fthat actively encourage diversity and
OL,15,Fequality.
OL,17,F"Prospect will be monitoring
OL,18,Fdevelopments at Google and other UK
OL,19,Femployers to make sure our members'
OL,20,Frights are protected," she added.
