OL,3,CGoogle scraps diversity hiring targets
OL,5,FSince Donald Trump moved into the Oval
OL,6,FOffice for a second time, there has
OL,7,Fbeen a pushback on DEI. In his first
OL,8,Fweeks as president, he has signed a
OL,9,Fflurry of executive orders relating to
OL,10,FDEI, including dialling back
OL,11,Ftransgender protections and ending
OL,12,Fgovernment programmes.
OL,14,FAfter the Washington DC plane crash in
OL,15,FJanuary, he suggested that the Federal
OL,16,FAviation Administration's "diversity
OL,17,Fpush" had made air travel less safe.
